{"tid":2023243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共武肺埋單條數初算","createTime":"2020-05-19T01:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T01:30:56.000Z","uid":319328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"175ff2da118054175a7d4d5ccf04e9bfee9421b6","tid":2023243,"uid":319328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"據芝大無厘斤教授估計，武漢肺炎硬掘美國每個家庭最少1皮美金 （7萬8港紙）。美國2019年有約1.28億個家庭，即合共1.28萬億美金（折合約10萬億港紙）。<br />\n<br />\n傳聞大陸2019年底揸1.1萬億美金美國國債。美國可以先走咗呢條數，再充公班愛國愛黨人士喺美國嘅資產填數，另加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/caseybmulligan/status/1262187558307577858?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaseybmulligan%2Fstatus%2F1262187558307577858%3Fs%3D21&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2Fy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=d01b78b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcaseybmulligan%2Fstatus%2F1262187558307577858%3Fs%3D21&h=3f5dafac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/caseybmulligan/status/1262187558307577858?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"6ae7010999284de1f83c9259769fc4c7baeeef8d","tid":2023243,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"順便捉埋班支共高幹子弟及家人啦<br />\n<br />\n所有資產都係貪返嚟"},{"pid":"68a30e29b1dc0d1e30612ae0d2b71179619fedbc","tid":2023243,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"清朝條數都賴皮唔還啦<br />\n美帝咪再軟 好返一定要狠狠咁報仇"}]}